snippet.title: Need for Speed The Run -- Run For The Hills Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: As The Run streaks through the hills of Nevada, you find yourself at the heart of the pack. Battling with the unforgiving desert heat and technically demanding terrain, you must do everything you can to fight your way to the front. IN STORES NOW: http://www.needforspeed.com/therun
